@@TJvCustomPreviewRenderer
Summary
  Base class for components that can render a print preview on a TJvCustomPreviewControl.
Description
  Use TJvCustomPreviewRenderer as a base class to derive from when you want to create
  components that can render a print preview. Override the abstract DoAddPage to create
  a print preview page by page.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomPreviewRenderer.CreatePreview
Summary
  Called when a preview should be created.
Description
  CreatePreview is called by a TJvCustomPreviewControl when the user wants to create a preview.
Parameters
  Append - True if the preview should be appended to the existing preview or false if
           a new preview should be created
Return value
  True if the preview could be created, false otherwise.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomPreviewRenderer.PrintPreview
Summary
  Specifies the print preview component that is associated with this renderer.
Description
  \Read PrintPreview to determine the TJvCustomPreviewControl or descendant that displays the preview
  created by the renderer.
